[Amit Varma]: of embarrassing him when I say that he is one of the people I most admire in modern

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:45.280
[Amit Varma]: India. J.P. is a rare public intellectual who, instead of complaining from the comfort

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:50.640
[Amit Varma]: of his armchair, as so many of us do, jumped into the rough and tumble of Indian politics

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:56.360
[Amit Varma]: to try and change the system from within. His journey in Indian politics has been fascinating,

00:02:56.360 --> 00:03:00.860
[Amit Varma]: and every time I speak to him, I feel like my brain is expanding and my understanding

00:03:00.860 --> 00:03:06.120
